songs.title: Desi Hip Hop Trap Freestyle
songs.lyrics:
Desi Hip Hop
Shayari is about to explain things

Mainu dil de tarazu naal tolo
Ve dujiya di suno nai aap tusi bolo
Eh gal tuhaddi theek
Main bhang te sharab peeke likhna va geet
Par geet jede likhde o hunde ne likhari
Likhari di jind hundi sari raat
Studio'ch band naale duniya to door
Chaaro paase gand pyaar mera ki kusoor
O maine jag nai banaya loki sadiya to pinde
Main nava nava aaya main kisi nu ki sikhana
Naale ik waari dhyaan nal suno mera gaana

Dil da tarazu leke jag naal tolo mera raaj ki
Aap tusi bolo
Bohemia Kehda Ae Ke… Desi Hip Hop

Namunkin Mere Bin, Mai Addictive Jive Heroine
Sihna Jive Shatrugan, Main..
Je Dharmendra Ramesh Sipy Nu Kehda Na Sholay Ch Jai Nu Bana do Amitabh Bachan
Aashqui, Mai Rahul Roy… Mere Baad Kihne Aashiq Aye..
Par Kihdi Gal Vich Vazan ??
Vajje Hip Hop Beat Jado Laptop Kadhan
Chup Chap Theek Munde Gal Karan, Fasan…
Mai Shahrukh, Jado Badla Rukh
Fer Loki Nukas Kive Kadhan ?
Mainu Sunn Loki Books Kyu Ni Kadhan ??
Meri Shayari Chon Hooks Kyu Ni Kadhan ??
Mai Te Kehna Hor Ageeh Vadhan, Mere Baad Hoge Kyu Khatam..
Ve Tenu Meri Kasam… Maine Jis Din Ton Ijaad Kita Desi Hip Hop
Theek Thakk… Ohde Baad Aish Kiti Din Raat, Future Meri Akhan Ch
Gina Note Jiven Tic Tock Pr Time Dase Na Meri G Shock
Desi Hip Hop...

Ring Ring.. Mera Phone Bajje Sari Raat…
Kudiyan De Call Aan, Naam Vi Ni Mainu Yaad..
Bardbaad Vairi Mere, Yaar Mere Aabad.. Mere Baad Loki Sare Rakhan Ge Yaad

Desi Hip Hop….. Desi Hip Hop……..

Namumkin Cheez Nai, Nale Sare Kisi Di Karde Rees Nai
Ve Saare Charso Bees Nahi, Par Ae Har Kisi De Bass Di Cheez Nai
Mai Batmeez Jiwe 2002 Ch Main
Ijaad Keta Jo, Mere Baad Kihne Karan Chale Hor
Mainu Ek Iak do jhede bol Kamm de Do
Ohde Baad Kaho Mainu Rap Chad, De do..
Liao Mainu Hor Koi Kam Dedo.. Mainu Ghum Na,,,
Jive Apeh Jamiya Nahio Jamna… Mere Warga…
Jive Jaado Likha Mai Geet, Mere Hath Ch Kalam Na.. Kalam Na…

Desi Hip Hop….. Desi Hip Hop……
